trans-unit.source: Represents configuration settings that enable use of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider"></xref> class for specific folders.
trans-unit.target: Representerer konfigurasjonsinnstillinger som aktiverer bruk av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider"> </xref> klasse for bestemte mapper.

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET build environment uses FolderLevelBuildProvider objects to generate source code for different file types and subfolders in an application.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET build-miljø bruker FolderLevelBuildProvider objekter til å generere kildekode for forskjellige filtyper og undermapper i en applikasjon.

trans-unit.source: Classes that are derived from the FolderLevelBuildProvider class generate source code for folders such as Bin, App_GlobalResources, App_LocalResources, App_WebReferences, App_Browsers, Theme, and for other custom folders.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som er avledet fra klassen FolderLevelBuildProvider Generer kildekode for mapper som biters mappene App_GlobalResources, App_LocalResources, App_WebReferences, App_Browsers, tema og andre egendefinerte mapper.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you do not create an instance of the FolderLevelBuildProvider class directly.
trans-unit.target: Du vanligvis ikke opprette en forekomst av klassen FolderLevelBuildProvider direkte.

trans-unit.source: Instead, you implement a class that derives from <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> and apply the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> class to it, and then configure the derived class for use in the ASP.NET build environment.
trans-unit.target: I stedet du implementere en klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>og bruke den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute>klasse til den, og Konfigurer den utledede klassen for bruk i ASP.NET build-miljøet.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> class targets folders instead of files.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute>klassen mot mapper i stedet for filer.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute>

trans-unit.source: You use instances of the FolderLevelBuildProvider class together with <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder> objects to build one or more files into a compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Du bruker forekomster av klassen FolderLevelBuildProvider sammen med <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder>objekter å bygge en eller flere filer i en kompilert samling.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The FolderLevelBuildProvider instance generates source code in the appropriate language for individual files, and the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder> object builds the source code contributed by each FolderLevelBuildProvider instance into a single assembly.
trans-unit.target: Forekomsten av FolderLevelBuildProvider genererer kildekode i det aktuelle språket for individuelle filer og <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder>objektet bygger kildekode bidro ved hver FolderLevelBuildProvider forekomst til en enkelt samling.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.AssemblyBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The FolderLevelBuildProvider class is specified in the `configuration` section of the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FolderLevelBuildProvider er angitt i den `configuration` -delen i Web.config-filen.
